[CATAPULT] Level [2] 50 charges (stats unaffected)
         (cannot wield weapons, cannot wear armor)

  The form of the catapult offers some interesting oppportunities for
  having fun. The ability to launch objects at other players for no
  apparent reason or for evil reasons altogether makes the catapult
  a perennial in-house gag.

>>-------------------------------ABILITIES-------------------------------<<

arm <object>   Load the catapult with something to shoot.

aim <player>   Aim the catapult at someone.

pull lever     Fire the contents of the catapult at the target.

